---
source: crates/test-framework/src/snapshot/mod.rs
description: "Query: tpch_q3"
---
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Federated                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |  Limit: skip=0, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |   Sort: revenue DESC NULLS FIRST, orders.o_orderdate ASC NULLS LAST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |     Projection: lineitem.l_orderkey, sum(lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - lineitem.l_discount) AS revenue, orders.o_orderdate, orders.o_shippriority                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |       Aggregate: groupBy=[[lineitem.l_orderkey, orders.o_orderdate, orders.o_shippriority]], aggr=[[sum(lineitem.l_extendedprice * (Int64(1) - lineitem.l_discount))]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |         Inner Join:  Filter: lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |           Inner Join:  Filter: customer.c_custkey = orders.o_custkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |             TableScan: customer projection=[c_custkey], full_filters=[customer.c_mktsegment = Utf8("BUILDING")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |             Filter: orders.o_orderdate < CAST(Utf8("1995-03-15") AS Date32)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |               TableScan: orders projection=[o_custkey, o_orderdate, o_orderkey, o_shippriority]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |           Filter: lineitem.l_shipdate > CAST(Utf8("1995-03-15") AS Date32)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |             TableScan: lineitem projection=[l_discount, l_extendedprice, l_orderkey, l_shipdate]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
| physical_plan | SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |   CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |     BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |       VirtualExecutionPlan name=duckdb compute_context=/tmp/tpch-duckdb_customer_benchmark.db;/tmp/tpch-duckdb_lineitem_benchmark.db;/tmp/tpch-duckdb_nation_benchmark.db;/tmp/tpch-duckdb_orders_benchmark.db;/tmp/tpch-duckdb_part_benchmark.db;/tmp/tpch-duckdb_partsupp_benchmark.db;/tmp/tpch-duckdb_region_benchmark.db;/tmp/tpch-duckdb_supplier_benchmark.db initial_sql=SELECT "lineitem"."l_orderkey", sum(("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount"))) AS "revenue", "orders"."o_orderdate", "orders"."o_shippriority" FROM "customer" INNER JOIN "orders" ON (("customer"."c_custkey" = "orders"."o_custkey") AND (("customer"."c_mktsegment" = 'BUILDING') AND ("orders"."o_orderdate" < CAST('1995-03-15' AS DATE)))) INNER JOIN "lineitem" ON (("lineitem"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey") AND ("lineitem"."l_shipdate" > CAST('1995-03-15' AS DATE))) GROUP BY "lineitem"."l_orderkey", "orders"."o_orderdate", "orders"."o_shippriority" ORDER BY "revenue" DESC NULLS FIRST, "orders"."o_orderdate" ASC NULLS LAST LIMIT 10 |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
